snippet.title: The Dungeon of Naheulbeuk: The Amulet of Chaos - The Goblins' Den (PC Gaming Show Extended Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Add the Dungeon of Naheulbeuk: The Amulet of Chaos to your Steam wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/970830/The_Dungeon_Of_Naheulbeuk_The_Amulet_Of_Chaos/

The Dungeon of Naheulbeuk: The AMulet of Chaos appeared today in the PC Gaming Show livestream, with an exclusive message from the Magician's voice, Felicia Day (Supernatural, The Guild) and a short gameplay segment. Here is a longer version of that gameplay segment, so you can see more of the game!

Don't forget to follow us on social media if you don't want to miss any news about the game:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DearVillagers
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DearVillagers/
